column20: Prominent throughout - disputing second when not fluent 2 out - went second and 1 length down when left in lead last - pushed out and kept on well run-in(op 22/1)

Towards rear - badly hampered 1st - headway into midfield 3 out - keeping on when left in fourth last - not reach leaders(op 33/1)
Didn't jump with fluency - midfield - not fluent 3 out - not fluent 2 out - no impression when not fluent last(tchd 4/1)
Towards rear - hampered 1st - not fluent 3rd - no extra 2 out(tchd 25/1)
Took keen hold - prominent - weakened quickly before 2 out(op 33/1)
Didn't always jump with fluency - in rear throughout(op 200/1)
Led at steady pace - faced challenge after 4 out - clear after 3 out - not fluent 2 out - going okay and 1 length ahead when fell last
